      "topic": "From Cells to Organisms & Heredity",
      "phenomenon": {
        "week1": "How can a single cell become a whole human being?",
        "week2": "Why do different body parts look and act so differently if they all came from one cell?",
        "week3": "How do cells know what job to do?",
        "week4": "What happens when cells stop working together properly?",
        "week5": "Why do some siblings look alike while others look completely different?",
        "week6": "How do parents pass traits to their children without touching their DNA?",
        "week7": "Why do some traits skip generations?",
        "week8": "Synthesis & Assessment"
